title: Maid-sama! (2-in-1 Edition), Vol. 4: Includes Vol. 7 & 8
description: Misaki secretly participates in the maid café’s eating contest to save a coworker from keeping a promise that she never should’ve made in the first place. Then things unexpectedly heat up when a game called Love Trial forces Misaki to participate in various festival games with Usui—while holding hands!
author: Hiro Fujiwara
